<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Powell Parker — Founder, Rightful Returns Recovery</title>
<meta name="description" content="Powell Parker is the founder of Rightful Returns Recovery, a contingency-only surplus funds and forensic asset recovery firm operating in Texas, Arizona, and Georgia.">
<meta property="og:title" content="Powell Parker — Founder, Rightful Returns Recovery">
<meta property="og:description" content="West Texas roots. Faith-driven. Helping people claim what's rightfully theirs.">
<meta property="og:url" content="https://www.powparker.com/">
