<!-- WHAT DRIVES ME -->
<section class="drives-section" id="drives">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-eyebrow fade-in">What Drives Me</div>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Why I Do What I Do</h2>
    <div class="section-divider fade-in"></div>
    <div class="drives-grid fade-in">
      <div class="drives-photo">
        <!-- PHOTO SLOT: <img src="arizona-landscape.jpg" alt="Arizona"> -->
        <div class="photo-placeholder" style="height:100%;min-height:400px;">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="4" y="4" width="40" height="40" rx="2" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="4" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <path d="M4 30l10-10 8 8 6-6 16 14" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          Arizona / landscape photo
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="drives-content">
        <div class="section-eyebrow" style="color:rgba(201,168,76,0.6);">The Foundation</div>
        <h3 class="section-title">Built on Faith,<br>West Texas Grit</h3>
        <p>I grew up in Hereford, TX — where you learn early that your word is your bond and hard work isn't optional. Those values don't leave you when you move to the city. They just find a bigger arena.</p>
        <p>After years watching families lose their homes to foreclosure and then lose again — because nobody told them money was left over — I knew there was a better way. Rightful Returns Recovery was built to fix that.</p>
        <div class="pillars">
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">&#x1F64F;</div>
            <div class="pillar-title">Why We Kneel</div>
            <p>Faith grounds every decision. We're stewards of other people's money and trust. That's not taken lightly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">&#x1F91D;</div>
            <div class="pillar-title">Why We Stand</div>
            <p>Families deserve an advocate in their corner. We stand between them and the system until the job is done.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar">
